nodes.text: Jayelle, formerly known as JL-3621, was a human female who formerly served as a stormtrooper in Company 77 of the First Order. When the company was ordered to fire on innocent civilians at the Battle of Ansett Island, they all refused, and defected from First Order service. The company resided on the ocean moon Kef Bir, under the leadership of Jannah. Jayelle served as a mechanic in the tribe, helping to develop Jannah's first energy bow.
